snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator Multiplayer Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
PowerWash Simulator has just received Online CO-OP in our latest game update 0.7! Try out and give us feedback in this new multiplayer Beta. Play with a friend in Career Mode (2 Player Max) or up to a total of 6 players in Free Play mode!

Play PowerWash Simulator here: https://steamcommunity.com/app/1290000

Awesome content creators in trailer: 
https://twitter.com/ReadySetBen
https://twitter.com/ebonix
https://twitter.com/helloitskolo
https://twitter.com/PsychePlays
https://twitter.com/Sips_
https://twitter.com/Angory_Tom

For more pressure washing goodness subscribe to our channel!
Follow our Twitter for daily satisfying content: https://bit.ly/TwitterPWS
Join our Discord to join the conversation: https://discord.gg/powerwashsimulator
Follow us on TikTok for quick spray socials: https://bit.ly/PWSTikTok

#PowerWashSimulator #Powerwashing #Pressurewashing #Gaming #Games #IndieGame #IndieDev

We are FuturLab and can't wait for your to play the latest update for our power washing game!
